description:
Sparkles ✨ because it’s Friday & we can get on the 🥂/🍸/🍺! It’s been so good to go out the past couple of weeks - but I hope the ‘old normal’ makes a return soon, because nothing beats moving through a packed bar to meet friends, or the energy you get from hundreds of other people packed in to a live gig. I’m looking forward to those times again...
Happy weekend ✨
